### 1. GET All Tasks (Success)
GET http://localhost:8080/tasks
X-API-KEY: secret12345
Accept: application/json

### 2. GET Single Task by ID (Success)
GET http://localhost:8080/tasks?id=1
X-API-KEY: secret12345
Accept: application/json

### 3. GET Task - Not Found (Error)
GET http://localhost:8080/tasks?id=999
X-API-KEY: secret12345
Accept: application/json

### 4. GET Task - Invalid ID (Error)
GET http://localhost:8080/tasks?id=abc
X-API-KEY: secret12345
Accept: application/json

### 5. POST Create New Task (Success)
POST http://localhost:8080/tasks
X-API-KEY: secret12345
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Finish Go Assignment"
}

### 6. POST Create Task - Missing Title (Error)
POST http://localhost:8080/tasks
X-API-KEY: secret12345
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": ""
}

### 7. PATCH Update Task (Success)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/tasks?id=1
X-API-KEY: secret12345
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "done": true
}

### 8. Unauthorized Access (Error)
GET http://localhost:8080/tasks
Accept: application/json

### 9. Wrong API Key (Error)
GET http://localhost:8080/tasks
X-API-KEY: wrong-password
Accept: application/json